            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="0"/>
                <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="line"/> <lb n="1"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/><supplied reason="lost">Get</supplied>ae et Iu<supplied reason="lost">liae Domnae Augus</supplied><lb break="no" n="2"/><supplied reason="lost">ta</supplied>e matri <expan><abbr>Aug<am>g</am></abbr><ex>ustorum</ex></expan> <supplied reason="lost">et castrorum</supplied> <lb n="3"/><supplied reason="lost">Io</supplied>vi Optimo <expan><abbr>Max</abbr><ex>imo</ex></expan> Iu<supplied reason="lost" cert="low">noni Reg(inae) Minervae</supplied> <lb n="4"/><supplied reason="lost">Sa</supplied>luti <expan><abbr>Mar</abbr><ex>ti</ex></expan> Patri <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <lb n="5"/><supplied reason="lost">Vic</supplied>toriae Aug<del rend="erasure"><expan><abbr>g</abbr><ex>ustorum</ex></expan></del> F<supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>ortun</abbr><ex>ae</ex></expan>? <expan><abbr>Red</abbr><ex>uci</ex></expan>? devic</supplied><lb break="no" n="6"/><supplied reason="lost">tis</supplied> <expan><abbr>host</abbr><ex>iis</ex></expan> voto sol<supplied reason="lost">uto dedicavit</supplied> <lb n="7"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> Hermes Gent<supplied reason="lost">iano et Basso</supplied> <lb n="8"/><expan><abbr>co</abbr><ex>n</ex></expan><supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ulibus</ex></expan></supplied><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <expan><abbr>Cal</abbr><ex>endas</ex></expan> M<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Ergänzungsvorschlag nach CIL III 10109. Am Anfang werden die Namen von Caracalla und Geta wohl im Genitiv hinter &amp;quot;&amp;quot;pro salute&amp;quot;&amp;quot; gestanden haben.</p>
